### Nossa Grana — testes da API (REST Client / VS Code)
### Rode na ordem: register -> guarda tokens -> usa workspaceId

@host = http://localhost:3333/api

### Health
GET http://localhost:3333/health

### 1) Registrar (cria usuário + workspace pessoal)
# @name register
POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria@exemplo.com",
  "password": "senha-super-secreta",
  "name": "Maria"
}

###
@access = {{register.response.body.accessToken}}
@refresh = {{register.response.body.refreshToken}}

### Login (se já registrado)
# @name login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "maria@exemplo.com", "password": "senha-super-secreta" }

### Usuário atual
GET {{host}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Listar workspaces
# @name workspaces
GET {{host}}/workspaces
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

###
@ws = {{workspaces.response.body.workspaces.0.id}}

### Criar conta corrente
# @name conta
POST {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Nubank", "type": "CHECKING", "openingBalance": 1000 }

###
@accId = {{conta.response.body.account.id}}

### Listar categorias (criadas por padrão)
# @name cats
GET {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Criar uma despesa
POST {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "{{accId}}",
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "amount": 120.50,
  "description": "Mercado",
  "date": "2026-06-20"
}

### Conta a pagar (PENDING + dueDate)
POST {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": "{{accId}}",
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "status": "PENDING",
  "amount": 89.90,
  "description": "Internet",
  "date": "2026-07-10",
  "dueDate": "2026-07-10"
}

### Listar transações
GET {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Contas a pagar
GET {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/transactions/payables?kind=payable
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Resumo do dashboard
GET {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/forecast/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Previsão
GET {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/forecast
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Sync pull (delta completo)
GET {{host}}/workspaces/{{ws}}/sync/pull
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Refresh token (rotação)
POST {{host}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refreshToken": "{{refresh}}" }
